<SYNC Start=244168><P Class=KRCC>
네
<SYNC Start=244919><P Class=KRCC>
좋아, 그럼
<SYNC Start=246728><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=247720><P Class=KRCC>
아니에요
<SYNC Start=249815><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249883><P Class=KRCC>
